---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/experience.css";
---

<BaseLayout title="Experience" page="professional">
  <div class="page page-professional">
    <section class="experience-hero">
      <h1>Experience</h1>
      <p class="experience-subhead">
        A summary of my professional background, focused on backend systems,
        architecture, and production ownership.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="experience-section">
      <h2>Experience</h2>

      <div class="timeline">
        <article class="timeline-item current">
          <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>

          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>

          <div class="experience-card">
            <div class="experience-content">
              <header class="experience-header">
                <h3>Principal Software Engineer</h3>
                <span class="experience-company">
                  XTIUM (formerly EvolveIP)
                </span>
                <span class="experience-dates"> 2026 - Present </span>
              </header>

              <ul class="experience-points">
                <li>
                  Served as lead developer across three strategic initiatives:
                  a VoIP provisioning and configuration management web app, an
                  SSO provider, and a data warehouse effort.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Set technical direction, coordinated implementation across
                  backend and frontend work, and drove delivery through the
                  full SDLC from design and planning to rollout and support.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Led cross-company initiatives that required alignment across
                  product, SRE, support, security, and adjacent engineering
                  teams to meet shared business and operational goals.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Balanced platform modernization with process improvement,
                  maintainability, and long-term system ownership across
                  multiple high-impact efforts.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <details class="experience-deep-dive">
                <summary>
                  <span>Deep dive</span>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path
                      d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      stroke-width="2"></path>
                  </svg>
                </summary>

                <div class="deep-dive-content">
                  <p>
                    In this role, I moved beyond single-project delivery and
                    acted as a lead developer across multiple related systems
                    that supported core platform capabilities and internal
                    operations.
                  </p>

                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      Led the technical execution of a
                      <strong>VoIP provisioning and configuration management web app</strong>,
                      helping modernize legacy workflows and improve visibility
                      into long-running operational tasks.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Drove development of an <strong>SSO provider</strong>,
                      shaping authentication flows, access boundaries, and
                      integration patterns aligned with enterprise identity
                      requirements.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Contributed lead development guidance to a
                      <strong>data warehouse initiative</strong>, helping define
                      how operational data could be organized, surfaced, and
                      used more effectively across the business.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Helped strengthen <strong>SDLC practices</strong> across
                      projects by shaping planning, delivery expectations,
                      implementation standards, and the handoff into support and
                      operations.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Established architecture and implementation patterns that
                      could be shared across projects instead of allowing each
                      effort to drift into its own siloed approach.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Worked directly with stakeholders across engineering,
                      product, support, operations, and other company groups to
                      keep cross-company initiatives focused on business value
                      and production realities.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Owned execution quality across projects, mentoring through
                      implementation details while maintaining a strong bar for
                      maintainability, reliability, and operability.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </details>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2022</div>

          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>

          <div class="experience-card">
            <div class="experience-content">
              <header class="experience-header">
                <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
                <span class="experience-company">
                  XTIUM (formerly EvolveIP)
                </span>
                <span class="experience-dates"> Jul 2022 - 2026 </span>
              </header>

              <ul class="experience-points">
                <li>
                  Led development of a next-generation provisioning platform,
                  modernizing a complex legacy VoIP configuration system.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Designed event-driven workflows with real-time user feedback
                  for long-running provisioning operations.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Owned both backend and frontend development, collaborating
                  closely with product, SRE, and support teams.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Integrated SSO, enhanced reporting, and AI-powered assistance
                  to improve usability and operational efficiency.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <details class="experience-deep-dive">
                <summary>
                  <span>Deep dive</span>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path
                      d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      stroke-width="2"></path>
                  </svg>
                </summary>

                <div class="deep-dive-content">
                  <p>
                    This initiative was started to address scaling limitations,
                    fragmented UX, and operational risk in a long-running legacy
                    provisioning platform used for enterprise VoIP services.
                  </p>

                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      Designed and implemented a background provisioning engine
                      using <strong>Temporal</strong>, enabling deterministic
                      workflows with live status streaming back to the UI.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Re-architected identity and access management using
                      <strong>SSO and role-based permissions</strong>, aligning
                      with enterprise security requirements.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Built real-time user feedback mechanisms for provisioning
                      steps, significantly improving transparency and
                      supportability.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Integrated an <strong>AI-powered assistant</strong> using
                      MCP tooling to provide application-specific context,
                      reducing support load and improving user experience.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Acted as lead developer on the new platform, guiding
                      architectural decisions and working directly with product
                      owners and support teams to refine workflows.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Collaborated closely with SRE to adopt and operate modern
                      tooling, including Kubernetes, ArgoCD, CI/CD pipelines,
                      and cloud infrastructure.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </details>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2020</div>

          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>

          <div class="experience-card">
            <div class="experience-content">
              <header class="experience-header">
                <h3>Associate Programmer</h3>
                <span class="experience-company"> AudioCARE Systems </span>
                <span class="experience-dates"> Apr 2020 - Jul 2022 </span>
              </header>

              <ul class="experience-points">
                <li>
                  Maintained and enhanced a suite of ~20 legacy applications
                  under strict government compliance requirements.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Worked across multiple systems and interfaces used by
                  healthcare and federal data platforms.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Contributed to platform modernization efforts and adoption of
                  modern development tooling.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Led the conversion of terminal-based applications into a
                  React-based internal web interface.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <details class="experience-deep-dive">
                <summary>
                  <span>Deep dive</span>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path
                      d="M6 8l4 4 4-4"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      stroke-width="2"></path>
                  </svg>
                </summary>

                <div class="deep-dive-content">
                  <p>
                    AudioCARE Systems supported healthcare and government
                    clients, requiring strict adherence to compliance,
                    reliability, and delivery timelines.
                  </p>

                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      Maintained and enhanced a diverse set of legacy
                      applications with varying architectures and technology
                      stacks.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Worked on interfaces enabling applications to integrate
                      with external data platforms across different customer
                      environments.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Assisted in migrating products onto a newer development
                      platform, improving maintainability and consistency.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Played a key role in modernizing internal workflows by
                      introducing tools such as Git, VS Code, and Jira.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Became the primary developer responsible for converting
                      terminal-based applications into a React-based web
                      interface used internally by staff.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </details>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="experience-section">
      <h2>Education</h2>

      <article class="education-card">
        <h3>B.S. in Computer Science</h3>
        <span class="education-school">
          University of Advancing Technology
        </span>
        <span class="education-date">2019</span>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="experience-section">
      <h2>Certifications</h2>

      <div class="cert-grid">
        <article class="cert-card placeholder">
          <div class="cert-badge empty">+</div>
          <div class="cert-body">
            <h3>Upcoming Certification</h3>
            <span class="cert-meta">Planned</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
